{"tid":1838585,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"問題癥結不在武漢肺炎有多嚴重，而在沒有一個屬於人民的政府","createTime":"2020-01-24T05:32:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T08:41:14.000Z","uid":81236,"like":60,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"dc7a89966ae4ad52b3e2dea74938bec95a32cfe1","tid":1838585,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:32:02.000Z","msg":"可能認為病情也關政治事扯太遠<br />\n<br />\n但病情的蔓延絕對與政府管治失信息息相關<br />\n<br />\n經濟向好時出賣你的民主<br />\n<br />\n經濟下行時出賣你的人權<br />\n<br />\n前兩項你可以置不理<br />\n<br />\n但原來平日對政權的放任<br />\n<br />\n疫情爆發時出賣你的健康<br />\n<br />\n試想<br />\n<br />\n今天出現武漢肺炎<br />\n明年可以有廣州腦炎<br />\n後年可以有北京眼炎<br />\n<br />\n可能性有太多<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎傳染性、死亡率有多高不是問題癥結<br />\n<br />\n真正問題在於一個不代表人民的政府<br />\n<br />\n香港如是，中國亦如是<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">普選吧</span></span><br />\n<br />\n以制度選出一個代表人民的政府<br />\n<br />\n無論在政治、經濟、生活、健康<br />\n<br />\n都必定以人民的權利為依歸<br />\n<br />\n別再說政治唔關我事<br />\n<br />\n政治可以剝奪你的金錢、自由<br />\n<br />\n現在在剝奪你的健康<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n評論人：唔好放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b07710a28701137409f07e4581d1e93866ad8b16","tid":1838585,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:34:54.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0402e3ee2feb6c75458d89139228b4519119c343","tid":1838585,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:37:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"793158b26217e794c2ee6a254c14242b38bd57e6","tid":1838585,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:38:07.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1668f9e0fc123